      <title>高盛利润超出预期，因债券销售推动投资银行业务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/goldman-sachs-profit-jumps-45-investment-banking-strength-2024-10-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受债券销售、股票发行和并购活动反弹的推动，高盛第三季度利润超出预期，其股价周二上涨逾 3%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/goldman-sachs-profit-jumps-45-investment-banking-strength-2024-10-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 11:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
